title: On our way to the trippe diggits! Join in :D

embed.description: Setting up my stream - more to come soon!

body: My name is Luke, I go by the IGN of Tactical Tantrum, and I'm mostly streaming League of Legends live for you, yes, YOU! Totally free of charge, that is! So come in, sit down, join me on my way! We'll have a great time together. Enjoy the high quality and the awesome overlay. I'm online right now so join in!
